# Daily Expense Analytics Dashboard

A React-based personal finance tracker built for the **Naan Mudhalvan Arts Internship Program 2026**.

## Features
- Add income & expense transactions
- 8 spending categories with icons
- Real-time balance summary cards
- Pie chart & bar chart analytics
- Filter, edit, and delete transactions
- Indian Rupee (₹) formatting

## Tech Stack
- React 18 + Vite
- Recharts (charts)
- CSS-in-JS (inline styles)

## Run Locally

```bash
npm install
npm run dev
```

Open [http://localhost:5173](http://localhost:5173)

## Build for Production

```bash
npm run build
```
